  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Celgosivir in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Genotype 1 Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Randomised, Dose-Ranging, Open-Label, Multi-Centre Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Celgosivir for 12 Weeks in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C Infection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
