  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  The patient must be 18 to 65 years of age, inclusive.

          -  Primary diagnosis of chronic HCV infection.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who did not respond or relapsed following therapy with interferon.
      </textblock>
